name: Five Nights at Obama's (WarmCokeCola)
description:
OOOGA BOOGA!!!! Scary FNAF fangame!

Welcome to the white house, friend. Obama took the wrong medications and needs to be watched over night.

Credits go to Scott Cawthon: Dude made FNAF. No Scott, no ballin Obama.

If you hate this game, comment "Ham & cheese without the greens" and leave.

If you think the game is a masterpiece, then good for you, you're awesome!
